commit.message:
Add an option to wait for a match

Fixes #16.

Flush pending requests synchronously

Based on wmutils/core@dd268ecacc773aa6f767f8d3e6653b2a71f25c4e.

Fixes #15.
Fixes #14.

Add {key,button}_{press,release}, pointer_motion

The *key* and *button* actions didn't work, because the press and
release events must be separated by a small amount of time.
Check WM_NAME length before copying to avoid garbage

Fix code style

- Indent with tabs, align with spaces.
- Always use braces when using control structures.

Apply actions to the whole window tree

This is necessary for re-parenting window managers.
Don't skip '-r' as a single filter
Close windows via the _NET_CLOSE_WINDOW client message
